query:
UPDATE challenge_daily_trackings
            SET
                day_of_program = $1,
                quantity_per_set = $2,
                quantity_of_set = $3,
                unit_id = $4,
                weight = $5,
                weight_unit_id = $6,
                note = $7,
                habit_id = $8,
                order_in_day = $9
            WHERE id = $10
